{"tid":663235,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［中國又贏］愛迪達行政總裁：鞋類生產繼續從中國轉往越南","createTime":"2018-05-13T06:32:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-13T07:01:27.000Z","uid":48083,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8454160e46800cd419797a990516b7c96d82f087","tid":663235,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T06:32:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/13/143206_217014114827c5fb4b53fabd6e1ac386.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F13%2F143206_217014114827c5fb4b53fabd6e1ac386.png&h=22da51fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n德國運動品公司愛迪達(Adidas)的行政總裁預計，愛迪達將繼續把制鞋生產線從中國轉移到越南，不過他對美國對中國製造的鞋類產品徵收關稅的可能表示不值得擔心。<br />\n<br />\n卡斯帕羅斯德(Kasper Rorsted)星期三在年度股東大會上表示，2017年越南工廠生產的愛迪達鞋類產品的比例為44％，高於2012年的31％，而中國供應商的比例為19％，低於2012年的30％。<br />\n<br />\n羅斯德說，&ldquo;不排除這種趨勢將繼續下去。&rdquo;他還說：&ldquo;無論貿易關稅如何，中國仍是一個重要的採購市場。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n羅斯特指出，至於哪些行業可能面臨新的美國關稅，仍有很大的不確定性。 &ldquo;我們可能會被徵收進口關稅，但我們的競爭對手也面對同樣的情況。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n愛迪達的競爭對手彪馬（Puma）大約三分之一的產品都是在中國生產的，彪馬上個月表示，它正在制定應急計畫，如果美國增收關稅，公司就會把部分生產線從中國轉移到其他亞洲市場。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.voacantonese.com/amp/4390957.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.voacantonese.com%2Famp%2F4390957.html&d=I4UYGyOFC9GC9oh4YvWiirZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=e97e844b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.voacantonese.com/amp/4390957.html</a>"},{"pid":"e211a01b90349639513f00404359483162f0a84a","tid":663235,"uid":54337,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T06:38:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/13/143756_819112c12de3e5baba111d98b537490b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F13%2F143756_819112c12de3e5baba111d98b537490b.png&h=65834705&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"71a777af53a3f514afee1037b7909fd6c7663784","tid":663235,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T06:39:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n深化改革成功了"},{"pid":"d5fddb03435bd5b20a41d4f867ee300efbc96d8e","tid":663235,"uid":12526,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T06:52:26.000Z","msg":"成功驅除外國勢力 中蟈又贏"},{"pid":"df16be56f6e1a2da2c494affd6d10b202776b02f","tid":663235,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T06:56:24.000Z","msg":"睇左 愛迪生"},{"pid":"2a94e653ca907c546a5a72840dcf127ae519e91f","tid":663235,"uid":82640,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T07:01:27.000Z","msg":"但Clark已經由越南搬去印度<br />\n<br />\n講真睇實英國老牌子啲廠點搬<br />\n係領先歐陸同美國好多年<br />\n00年代Clark喺越南開廠<br />\n10年代Clark由越南搬去印度開廠<br />\n<br />\n中國就算吧啦<br />\n日本價錢<br />\n印度質素"}]}